{"tid":1464061,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(巴絲冷靜)場運動已經俾林奠睇死咗","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:30:30.000Z","uid":235875,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c29d555229e476f18d7d2f537921c78076aeb42c","tid":1464061,"uid":235875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:20:43.000Z","msg":"自殺同被捕人士我地仲未還返個公道俾佢地，已經睇到雨傘失敗嘅影子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>犬隻25仔戰術</strong>，成功挑起大家神經。<br />\n<strong>機管局出招</strong>令旅客對示威者矛盾增加。<br />\n再加上經兩日互相指責，割蓆同block行為情況非常嚴峻。我地係咪唔記得5大訴求??<br />\n好多人都話唔塞都塞咗咁你想點?冷氣軍師出黎現場先講。坦白講我係有黎現場既，學某巴絲話：其實唔洗封曬佢，只要留一個入口俾佢地入去已經可以。等佢地自己排，又可以減少同遊客對抗，而家做都未遲。<br />\n新聞鏡頭全部睇到遊客同示威者拉鋸同解釋，會輸咗個形象。<br />\n我強烈建議要定一個<span style=\"color: red;\">全港道歉日或者機場道歉日</span>將之前不合作運動同受影響遊客睇到，勉回返大家既信任。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">犬隻射盲人，林奠都唔割。我地塞一塞同包圍公安就即割?</span>大家唔好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你同我都有喊過，然後不了了之?場運動係長期抗爭。<br />\n今次輸咗香港人會更加政治冷感。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">818我會出黎</span><br />\n<br />\n喚起返大家一開始走出黎既心態。希望大家睇到"},{"pid":"d3c5a5468ac1c87fd568cef0dcb3049e72948ab9","tid":1464061,"uid":235875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:21:52.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"1ad0acce82b4865a413a3b0c60ee337f05234169","tid":1464061,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:22:52.000Z","msg":"所有人都係手足，只係每個人都有盲點位only<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"cfbd9a347eea4f772e03accd2991a2079e6afa02","tid":1464061,"uid":235875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"推9"},{"pid":"9e992c2c9dac2a40aba0229153996e516dc2e045","tid":1464061,"uid":274141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"8.18當日可以順便整「罷工」問卷 [幫手推比民陣睇]<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463566\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463566</a>"},{"pid":"fc6168930b096a1b17c2017979760704b5a8cdea","tid":1464061,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:25:39.000Z","msg":"8.13機場策略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463429</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a8e4a0f5ca328e71095250c9028f9a4ba0f7df5d","tid":1464061,"uid":235875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:55:42.000Z","msg":"推8"},{"pid":"61e72bad73ac44d9b40f0ba068fc316ce1c25bcf","tid":1464061,"uid":235875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"推7"},{"pid":"da788fb76f1415d08287354dba66c728727992dd","tid":1464061,"uid":235875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"e133b7031751a08b0963e32eacf1efa968355d33","tid":1464061,"uid":207942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba0b02edc9cf5d1f81fe0b145493dc2cf3390306","tid":1464061,"uid":235875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:09:12.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"971a79646ce0575533e9bb9a7b6dc2ac08e0fb46","tid":1464061,"uid":204429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:15:23.000Z","msg":"而家贏緊"},{"pid":"776ef500b23a43881a6d42b6e1b7a4a0b0c4253f","tid":1464061,"uid":90421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c2655370f